The Quintesson murmurs something to himself, obviously interested in
Autofire, when Megatron walks in. "All right Autofire, see if the chips
Galvatron inserted into me is still there. If it is, take it out." he
asked, he then looked at the Quintesson, "YOu can help him".

The Quintesson breaks out of his thought, "Yes Megatron" it says, without
emotion.
